 again, I run out of range....wait a minute he isnt hitting me. Turn to look at him..he isnt chasing me. So I click my epic which has a charge in it. He summons me and interrupts it. Now I am standing under him and retry the epic. 20 seconds is a very very long time. Epic arrives in the same split second he hits me taking me down to 1 bubble of hp. Pet jumps on him while i run around the room screaming again. He DIES! Joy in EQland. Tried to summon group back in to get their marks, no joy. Didnt know about the fact you can get in to loot him as the trial resets 30ish minutes later right before his body poofs. Anyway I actually heard a jasjen so ubah out of that adventure. Was T H E most fun I have had in EQ in prolly a year. Quite a bit of info hidden in the story for all you aspiring trialers. (i made that word up i think)<br>
